name: Emerald Green
description:
Flower Dust Plug Series. 

A simple but pretty little dahlia flower dust plug to adorn your smart phone! Be it an iPhone, iPod, Samsung phones and any other cellphones as long as it has a 3.5 mm jack, the stopper will fits perfectly! 

The flower sized at 15 mm and attached to a black stopper.

name: Gold Amethyst
description:
Amethyst String Bracelet Collection - 001

A simple purple string bracelet adorned with five 6mm 24K gold plated glass beads and finished off with 20K gold plated crimp bead and gold plated seed beads. 

Great for stacking but also looks good all by its own.
Simply tie a knot or two after adjusting the bracelet to secure it on your wrist.

The bracelet measured approximately at 22 cm / 8.6 inches. 
String is made from Super-Lon string. 


*Made to order*
Please allow 1-2 weeks of processing before shipping.
